%?mv(5)<%?St(battery display)<%Vd(title)|%Vd(titlebat)>|%?St(battery display)<%?mp<%Vd(clock)|%Vd(clock)|%Vd(clock)|%Vd(title)|%Vd(title)>|%?mp<%Vd(clock)|%Vd(clock)|%Vd(clock)|%Vd(titlebat)|%Vd(titlebat)>>>

# Viewport for main title (without battery %)
%Vl(title,7,0,369,21,2)%Vf(000000)
%s%al%Sx(FM Radio)

# Viewport for title when battery % is shown
%Vl(titlebat,7,0,316,21,2)%Vf(000000)
%s%al%Sx(FM Radio)

# Viewport for clock display
%Vl(clock,7,0,316,21,2)%Vf(000000)
%t(10)%s%al%Sx(FM Radio);%t(30)%s%al%?cf<%cH:%cM|%cl:%cM %cP>

